    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus of Old World tropical trees and shrubs of the madder family (Rubiaceae), containing more than 140 species. Gardenias have fragrant, tubular, white or yellow flowers, evergreen leaves, and berry-like fruit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
